<br>
Jamil and I have been speaking recently of a desire to acquire a new monk weapon. This weapon is known as the Fist of Horn. Thanks to the graciouness of a passing Paladin, I am already in possession of one, and I can attest to it's formidable power. <br>
<br>
In my researching of this weapon, I have concluded that it is only available on the moon in an area known as the Paludial Caverns. It is given up by The Reishicyben which actually resembles a very large mushroom or so I was told. I have recently returned from a scouting trip of the area. This area would be far to powerful for simply Jamil and I alone so we are coming to our brothers and sisters for assistance.<br>
<br>
((ooc stuff))<br>
A possible date for this would be after 2/16. The zone itself is not too horribly difficult for those above level 20. According to Allakhazam it's not heavy on the loot, but is a great area for experience. The 'shroom spawns every 90 minutes, and with the low server population we shouldn't have any difficulty ruling the entire zone. There appear to be areas suited for levels 12-25 or so. Granted that information could be wrong, it would be best to plan for 2 groups split between mid-teen and early to mid 20's of course the more the merrier, and if there are others that want to make the journey, invite them along. <br>
<br>
If by any chance, there is a mid-teen group that wants to try to tackle some of the areas earlier, please message me. I am chopping at the bit to tackle some of these Luclin zones even though it can be a bit laggy.<br>
<br>
-Malackai<br>
15th Season Monk of the Ashen Order <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=20371A><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/uebine.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ebine</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#660000>(2/1/02 2:58:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=251.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Moon Raid (x-post from Brothers board)</span><hr size=1> For our info. <br>
